  "text": "The TKF91 [CITATION_1] model has several parameters. Thus, it initially seemed inevitable to carry out the non-trivial computations for filling DP cells from scratch for each individual cell. However, after analyzing which expressions are constant and can thus be pre-computed and reused (i.e., memoized), we reduced the operations required for calculating a DP cell value to just three: indirection, summation, maximum.",
